source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/black-bean-and-poblano-flautas-60196d55c53c034a3c088c7f
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
  calories: 970 kcal
